{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/scene_bg.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"},{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/scene_21.png","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/scene_21.png","visible":"hide"}]},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/scene_22.png","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaFront"}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_23182.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":240202,"motion":1,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day22.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime02","chara":[{"id":240202,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-1"}],"nameAvCenter":"Sayaka","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]Sorry for the wait.","textAvColor":"textSayaka","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":240202}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810600,"motion":400,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-2"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Hitomi","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]My! What a lovely flower!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-3"}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]This one's a kitty!@So, this is latte art?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":240202,"motion":100,"pos":0,"soulGem":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-4"}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Isn't it cool? My senpai here@at work at is like, a pro at this."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":240202,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-5"}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I've been learning how to do it too,@but I haven't really gotten the hang of it..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-6"}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]You've really been putting in your all@at the cake shop, huh?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":240202,"motion":201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-7"}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Well, I AM in need of money right now!"},{"chara":[{"id":240202,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-8"}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]If I can cheer up Kyosuke even a little bit@with some rare CDs, that'd be..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":810600,"motion":0,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-9"}],"nameAvRight":"Hitomi","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Wouldn't he...be upset by that?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":240202,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-10"}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Huh...?"},{"chara":[{"id":810600,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-11"}],"nameAvRight":"Hitomi","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]He may not be able to play the violin@ever again, after all..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":240202,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-12"}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...He was pretty depressed about it@at first."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":240202,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-13"}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":240202,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-14"}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I think he's been able to get this far@because of his love for music."},{"chara":[{"id":240202,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-15"}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So, I feel like music is going to be@his salvation in these tough times."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":810600,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-16"}],"nameAvRight":"Hitomi","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]You think music...will save him?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-17"}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]You really believe in him, don't you?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":240202,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-18"}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Well...I think it's more praying@and hoping, rather than believing."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":810600,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104211/vo_full_912122-010-19"}],"nameAvRight":"Hitomi","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":